## Git Workflow
- **ALWAYS** create feature branch before changes
- **NEVER** commit directly to main
- **Branch naming:** `feature/{description}` or `fix/{description}`
- Self-test before push: `scripts/test-local.sh`
- Monitor CI after push: `scripts/check-ci.sh`

## Business Logic Documents
<!-- Remove this section if not applicable -->
**Location:** `documents/01-business/` — SOURCE OF TRUTH

**Structure:** 3-layer per domain:
```
documents/01-business/{domain}/
  rules.md          # Business rules and constraints
  use-cases.md      # Use cases with actor, steps, errors
  api-contract.md   # API endpoints, request/response, error codes
```

**Rules:**
- Doc and code MUST be in the same PR
- Do NOT hardcode business rules — use config keys from rules.md

